OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChina reveals British      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fnational jailed for spying 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A British national was sentenced to    
OL,6, five years in jail for spying in 2022, 
OL,7, China's Ministry of Foreign Affairs    
OL,8, (Mofa) has now revealed.               
OL,10,FThe defendant - named as Ian J Stones -
OL,11,Fcommitted the "crime of illegally      
OL,12,Fobtaining intelligence for overseas    
OL,13,Factors", a Mofa spokesman said.        
OL,15,FThe spokesman added that he had        
OL,16,Fappealed against the sentencing but the
OL,17,Fcase was upheld last September.        
OL,19,FThis was only revealed in a Mofa       
OL,20,Fbriefing on Friday.                    
